      "content": "it's just so hard to imagine actually finding peace any other way. like, everything i try to do to \"move on\" just feels like more work i don't have the strength for. when you say i \"deserve\" to find peace like that... it almost sounds like you're saying it's a valid choice. like it's actually okay to just stop fighting?",
